    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 44-49.</p><p>Perfect Defense</p><p>Beginning at 22nd level, as long as you are wielding a weapon, you reduce the damage from weapon attacks by 10. In addition, whenever you are subject to an effect that allows you to make a Dexterity saving throw to take only half damage, you instead take no damage if you succeed and only half damage if you fail.</p></div>",
